[SN]TITLE[SN]
Gotham star Erin Richards has England v Wales Six Nations fever

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
Hollywood actress Erin Richards gets you fired up for Saturday's England v Wales Six Nations title-decider with a powerful translation of Welsh poem What is Man?

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
Media playback is not supported on this device
The Welsh Gotham star, who plays lead Barbara Kean in the hit US series, recites an English translation of Waldo Williams' iconic work ahead of Saturday's game at Twickenham that will send a tingle down your spine.
